Dialog: What do they think this is a freeway!?
Ah...can't...a man have a little peace around here, a little nap?
Ula Ule U'wama.
Lay a hand on me and I'll, take this five iron and wrap it around head!
Hold! We come in peace.
Oh, a sort of primitive peace corps! Well let's introduce each other. My name is Thurston Howell the third, what exactly is yours?
I, am KING Killiwani! Emperor of eternal night! Light of eternal day! Seeker of eternal truth! And lord of eternal eternalties!
Oh yes, keeper of eternal flame.
Oh a gas tycoon! Well I always like to do business with chairman of the board.
Amu wamu.
I'll come right to the point. Can you rescue us and take us back to civilization, and what exactly will it cost, ME.
Must find white goddess Winomi.
Yes well of course we'll discuss the scavenger hunt a little later. Now to rescue us would you say a fair price would be a...a...a thousand dollars?
No talk rescue!
I'll talk louder! Would you say, five thousand dollars?
Legend say that on eighth moon, white goddess Winomi will be found on island to west!
Wha...wha...why I know your changing the subject, driving a hard bargain. Well, I can be pushed so far! One hundred thousand dollars and that is my final offer!
Halu yama e'kwana!
Halu hala da'wama. Soon time for new year feast! Must find goddess Winomi!
Well let's settle this white goddess business. Where exactly, pray tell do we FIND her!?
Already find two! Problem is, only need one!
Oh you mean Ginger or Mary Ann! Now if one of them is the white goddess, you'll rescue us?
Ehhhhh
Oh joy I just saved one hundred thousand dollars!!
Oh Thurston look at these marvelous blooms...
Ahhhh!
Who are these persons? And what are they doing down there?
Ah Lovey I'd like you to meet his majesty, King Killiwani.
King?
Emperor of eternal night! Light of eternal day! Seeker of...
Eh...no need to go through all that again. He's really a king!
Oh Thurston royalty!
Eh...wait till he stands up, he's really king size.
Please your majesty do stand up!
Oh, this is truly island of white goddess.
Thurston did you hear that? What a charming thing for him to say. I wonder if he knows Grace and prince Rainier? Indeed an honor your majesty.
May I extend to you the hospitality of our little island.
I got'em I got'em tie'em up tie'em up!
Gilligan you dunts you did it again! These savages are civilized!
Forgive is your majesty, what a deplorable breach of protocol!
Here ah...the rear escape hatch.
...outrigger's doing here!? If I'm not mistaken it's the handy work of the primitive Papuan tribe. Oh I had no idea we where so near their island.
But professor ep...if they're so primitive, how did they get this?
It means they must have contact with civilization.
MUST have eternal flame!
Your highness!
Heh!
Is this your lighter?
Hah! You find eternal flame!!
Some keeper of eternal flame.
You like to join eternal ancestor!?
That's a fine lighter you have there your highness. Would you mind telling where you got it?
Hmmmm, sometime ship come, captain give me eternal flame, plus one can eternal lighting fluid.
You mean ships land on your island?
Some time. Got no time for talk now. Must start FIRE dance! You care to dance?
Ah...no thank you, I'm a, waltz man myself.
Heh...
YOU care to dance.
No I don't think so.
You DANCE!
Come to think of it I do need the practice!
Oh of course I'll be their little white goddess.  If it means a chance of getting off this silly island.
Oh Lovey we knew you'd cooperate!
Darling after all I've had so much experience. You remember at collage I was queen of the prune bowl parade!?
Pitted prune of course! Oh you'll make a lovely with goddess!
Oh thank you dear.
Are you ready for this! Guess who thinks she's a goddess!?
Would I be too far off if I guessed Mrs. Howell?
When I think of some women's ego, just makes me sick. I mean after all who'd make a better goddess than me?
Well ah...know that you brought it up. I could think of just one other person.
Who?
Me.
You!? Well your too short!
Well goddesses don't have to be tall! Why they just have to be...(pause)...like goddesses!
I'm surrounded by ego maniacs!
I...I have good news! Behold your white goddess!
This is the most thrilling moment of my life!
Your majesty! Here is your goddess!
Mine is the original!
Your Highness, guess what I found!?
Eh...Don't tell me.
The goddess, Winomi!
Heh, looks like we all came off the same rack!
What we do now.
Why don't you try, eeny meeny miney moe?
Good idea!
Eeny meeny miney moe Catch'em goddess by'em toe Soon to island back we go Eny meeny miny moe!
The Gods have spoken!
Oh now I've seen everything! You a goddess!?
Well I'm most capable of coping with the protocol involved! You see I was presented at the court of saint James.
Not to mention Prune Queen!
Pitted Prune Queen!
I think this whole contest is fixed!
And I know by whom! What I want to know is by how MUCH!
I've had enough!
MORE than enough!
Girls remember the big picture! We're going to be rescued!
Sore losers!
You make volcano God very happy!
Volcano God!
At end of ceremony you marry volcano.
Hey skipper, I never knew volcanoes could get married!
Big honor for goddess Winomi.
To be thrown into a volcano!?
No man is going to throw my wife into a volcano!
Wife? She your WIFE!?
Yes, I'm very honored!
Ehhh...too bad. Goddess Winomi must be maiden. Girl with mate can not be bride to volcano.
Oh Thurston thank you for being my mate!
Yes darling!
Must find ONE from other two!
You mean Ginger or Mary Ann?
I choose.
Oh no, wait a minute King! Now look, we don't like your rules so the game is over!
Over!?
That's right! We'd like to get you a white goddess but, you play too rough!!
I'm sorry this store is closed, try another market!
Nice going little buddy!
Thank you.
Your welcome.
Last word?
Definitely.
We go!
Perhaps if it was a shallow volcano.
Oh Thurston!
But we were going to be rescued if you'd just...heh...heh...heh...
Say those natives took it better than I thought they would!
I wonder where they went?
I don't know.
Must have white goddess by sundown!!
They've got poisonous blow guns!
Now I know what they went for!
One of your woman must go! Or take by force!
Poison or no poison, your going to get one of our girls over our dead bodies!
Oh he's so impetuous!
Oh skipper, can we lay down now?
Well I'm all for jumping 'em! There's only three of them and there's four of us.
Use your head skipper, just one poison dart and it would be three against three!
Yeah and another poison dart, three against two, and another poison dart three against one, and another poison dart three against...
Gilligan!
...none.
There must be some way of doing this without anyone getting hurt. Especially a Howell!
The only way to do that is to give 'em a white goddess.
Well they're not getting one of our girls!
Maybe they'd settle for a girl gorilla or something.
Oh that's the most ridiculous thing I ever...
Now wait a minute wait a minute. Perhaps we can trick them. Perhaps one of us could dress as...
A gorilla!?
No no no, as a woman.
Did I hear you right!?
Why not!? One of us could dress as a woman and volunteer to go with them.
Yeah and get thrown in a volcano!
Oh of course not! The rest of the men could follow in a raft and keep watch at a safe distance.
Oh and keep checking on any visiting ships that might be at their island!
Now wait a minute. Look around the table, you think that anyone of us could pass as a white goddess?
You have a better idea?
Well of course!
What is it?
Haven't thought of anything yet.
You need any help?
Wa...wa...no thank you Ginger bu...eh...I'm afraid I...I just killed your living girdle.
Come on out, let me have a look at you.
Well turn around.
Well what do you think?
Well ah...you've got nothing to worry about if they throw you the a volcano.
I don't!?
Eh...no it would through you right back!
Take a deep breath. Now hold still or I'll catch you in the zipper.
There!
Mary Ann. I'd like your candid opinion. Do you think that I could pass as a woman?
Well, it depends on two things.
Two things.
Mmm...mmm, How dark the night and how bad their eyesight.
Oh I'm sorry, I'm afraid I'm in the wrong...
Thurston have you gone out of your mind!? What are you doing in my wig and by best neg...negligee?
Well it's the only thing that fit you see and looked sheik at the same time.
I don't understand.
Well one of us men have to become the white goddess.
Awe darling you so gallant, your doing this to save the girls.
No I'm doing it to save my business. Get to that King's island, back to civilization. Eh...what do you girls do when your ear rings are pinching your ears?
Oh we just think of how much our shoes are pinching our feet!
I think I'm going to faint!
No no Lovey don't heh...heh leave us alone we have some serious girl talk.
Girl...Oh dear well, don't say anything catty girls just because I'm leaving first.
Ho...ho...ho...ho, Well I must say you two are a gruesome twosome!
You don't make us a thrillsome threesome I might add.
You know I don't think this is going to work.
Maxine, I don't know about you and Lavern, but I'm getting out of this.
Now wait a minute. Where's Gilligan? Gilligan. GILLIGAN!
Somebody call...me...
I'd hate to judge this beauty contest, because nobody'd win!
He might be able to pull it off.
Oh no! I'm not gonna dress up like a girl.
Oh yes you are, and that's an order.
I'm not gonna dress up like a girl and you can't make me...
...you can't make me, you can't make me!
We already did!
Gilligan if I ever saw a white goddess you are IT!
Yes I think that this just might work.
You look positively ravishing!
But what are we gonna call him? I mean who ever heard of a goddess named Gilligan?
Why don't you call her Gilliana? What am I says!?
Gilliana that's such...such a musical feminine abs...turn around move for us Gilliana!
They're killing me! I don't see how women wear them!
They think about how much their ear rings are pinching their ears.
Sun sink low in sky.
No more time. Must choose goddess now.
KING!!
Heh!
Have I got a goddess for you! Behold!
We forgot all about little Gilliana, she was...
...OUCH those heels!...was on the other side of the island picking berries. Ah...your highness, Gilliana, this is king Killiwani.
Emperor of night. Light of...
Yes we know...   GILLIGAN/GILLIANA (HIGH SQUEEKY VOICE) Charmed I'm sure. They tell me your looking for a white goddess.
Are you married woman?
Mar...married? I'm not even engaged.
Your highness is this a goddess or is this a goddess!?
The gods have chosen. You must go to them.
Well couldn't they come to my place?
Tonight, we have ceremony, make goddess official.
Ah hu ninee'pu
Ah hu ninee'pu
Ah hu haha'hu
Ah hu haha'hu
Ah hu haha'hu Ah hu haha'hu...
Goddess of night. Goddess of day. Goddess of work! Goddess of play. Goddess of moon, with pale white skin. Bride of volcano then throw her in!
Here. When tide come in, we leave.
Don't hurry on my account!
Psssst! Gilligan
Oh it's you skipper!
Keep up the good work your doing great!
I have a feeling the worst is yet to come!
Your right, he's coming up the path now! Put your wig back on!
Skipper don't leave me!
I'm not gonna leave ya, don't worry about a thing I'm just a whistle away!
Oh good.
Who is it?
King Killiwani!
Ah...come in!
Soon you come to my island!
Yes I know.
You no look happy.
I was thinking about my future husband the volcano. I don't think we're meant for each other.
Funny, me think same thing.
Your not gonna throw me in the volcano!?
You beautiful woman!
Your not so bad yourself.
Have you very much on my mind! Want you for my self!
How do you mean?
Throw dummy in volcano, keep you for me, make you my wife.
As soon as we follow Gilligan to the other island, we'll be back in civilization in no time!
Ah the sounds of civilization, the rustle of money as I make a deposit.
The sound of marching, as I drill our servants.
The (whistles) as I walk down the street.
Girls, Mr. And Mrs. Howell we've got to do something and do it quick!
Well what's wrong skipper!
It's the king, he's getting fresh with Gilligan!
Oh that cad that bounder!
If the king finds out that he's not a girl...I mean the wedding off the trip to the other island is off...th...the rescue is off!
Oh we we've got to keep him away from Gilligan!
Exactly! Mrs. Howell why don't you take that fruit over to him, keep him busy for a while!
Oh that's a good idea captain. I always did hear that the way to a man's stomach is through the kitchen. Or is it a way to a man's Heart? Oh it doesn't matter.
Never mind, please.
Mary Ann we can entertain him, I've got those darling dancing costumes from the U.S.O tour.
Oh great let's get started!
How 'bout you Mr. Howell can you do anything?
Well yes yes I can do some magic tricks, I just happen to have my magicians outfit...always carry it with me.
Well fine well why don't you go get it!
You don't go get a magician's outfit, you simply go SNAP of the fingers presto zingo zahpo!
...And there you are! The cape ha...ha!! See what I mean!?
Aren't you married?
Have thirty three wives. But they no understand me. Me lonely king.
Pretty knee!
Very pretty!
I'll show you something prettier!
Snack time, anybody for passion fruit!?
No...no...no not passion fruit!
Go, want to be alone!
I think I'll have a banana.
Oh shall I...ah peel it for you dear?
Out! Out!
Well if you feel that way it.
OUT!
Oh well ah...if you ah...change your mind let me know.
Out!
Well I'm going!
Killiwani have present for Winomi.
Ring belong to mother. Now give to you.
Your mother must have a very big fat finger.
Not for finger, for nose!
I'm sorry but my nose isn't pierced.
Oh, me fix that.
Why don't we wait till we know each other better! Here here take a bite!
Entertainment time!

Welcome to the club Tropicana!   MARY ANN & GINGER  (SINGING & DANCING) Dada da da Da DA! Won't you come home Bill Bailey. Won't you come home. I've moaned the whole day long. I'll do the cookin' honey. I'll pay the rent. I know I done you wrong.
Enough! Want to be alone!
Look who thinks he's Greta Garbo.
OUT!
And now!
For your pleasure!
We present!
The great!
The magnificent!
The super stupendous!
The most phenomenal magician of this or any time!      MARY ANN & GINGER Thurston Howell the third!
Yea! Yea! Yea! Yea! Yea! Yea! He knows a thousand tricks! And I want to see them all!
You only trick I interested in.
Mmmmy you're a fat one...now for my first trick...A simple deck of cards.
Now for my a...second trick!
An ordinary red a...handkerchief, you see...passing the magic hand...and it becomes a yellow handkerchief!
That not yellow!
Now for my final or block buster trick, a simple chapeau.
Understand? Nothing in chapeau. Right? Empty? Everyone see? Empty?
Now! Pull a rab...magic hand pull a rabbit out!
That rabbit?
You want to buy a duck?
OUT! Take friend with you, out!
First time I ever laid an egg.
Kiki kanda! Kiki kanda!
Guard door, keep all out.
How 'bout little kiss baby!?
No no no no no no no no! I'm not the kind of girl you think I am!
I know! Let's play hide and seek. And if you catch me I'll give you a great big kiss.
Kiss? That good game how you play?
You close your eyes and count to ten.
Uh...one two three four...
No no no no not so fast! We women can run around fast in heels!
One...two...three...four...five...six...seven...eight...
FOUR!
Five...six...seven...eight...
FOUR!
Five...six...seven...eight...
FOUR!
Five...six...seven...eight...
Nine ten! Ready or not here I come!
Where are you!? Where ARE you!? I'm coming in! No time for games! Yaaaaaah!
Buhula humba! Buhula humba!
Bahula humba what!?
Goddess vanish before very eyes! Nothing left but hair and dress!
I warn you before, gods angry! No make pass at goddess!
Bad magic here!
Leave this island!
We go now!
Gilligan. Where's Gilligan?
Goddess! Yo...your out of uniform!
It's no use Mr. Howell. They would have found out sooner or later I wasn't a girl.
Well you can't quite now, we need them to get rescued!
I hate being a girl, besides he was touching my knee!
Small price to pay for civilization! Come on boy! Follow me!
Wait! Wait! Come back! Come back!
Eh...take him with you! I...I mean take her with you! Quick goddess in...in to this in...in...in to your robe, here...here...here you are!
Mr. Howell it's no use.
No you look gorgeous gorgeous gorgeous!
I don't think so look!
I'm writing this adventure up in our log. Wonder how you spell king Killiwani?
K...I...N...G, king.
(sarcastically) Thanks a lot Gilligan!
Where you going with that!?
I'm outing it outside with the rest of your stuff!
What's going on here!?
Well I was a white goddess right!?
Well yeah wa...I guess you could say that.
And a goddess is royalty right!?
Well yes I guess so.
Well you don't expect us royalty to live with you commoners do you?
Oh Gilligan you put that chest down right NOW!
Yes sir.
